      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented release notes and regression test suite.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2021 R2 is a commercially validated solver with full version control, documented release history, and an internal regression test suite. Achieved level exceeds the MRL 2 requirement."
    },
