      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark problems with known analytical solutions demonstrate correct solver implementation for incompressible viscous flow.",
      "rationale": "Solver verified against lid-driven cavity and Poiseuille flow benchmarks. Numerical errors remain below 0.5% for all benchmark cases, confirming correct implementation of governing equations."
    },
