      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid properties) match simulation boundary conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data collected at matched flow rates (2–6 L/min) and rotational speeds. Blood analogue fluid viscosity and density match simulation inputs within 2%. Boundary condition fidelity confirmed."
