    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. Predicted relative hemolysis index agrees with experimental data within 8% across all five operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory decision for this Class II CPB device.",
